	measure 'Scatter Plot Color Ads' = ```
			
			VAR _maxCost = AVERAGEX(ALLSELECTED(factAds[Ad Name]), [Cost]) 
			VAR _maxRoas = Averagex(ALLSELECTED(factAds[Ad Name]), [ROAS]) 
			RETURN
			SWITCH(
			     TRUE(),
			     [Cost] > _maxCost && [ROAS] < _maxRoas, "#D64550", //red
			     [Cost] < _maxCost && [ROAS] > _maxRoas, "#118DFF", // blue
			     [Cost] < _maxCost && [ROAS] < _maxRoas, "#D9B300", //yellow
			     BLANK()
			     )
			```
		lineageTag: b8fa376f-6173-4726-a656-6a3aa242c823

